Package: tomics
Title: Useful functions for working with GWAS data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Thomas", "Willis", , "tom.willis@live.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains utility functions for working with GWAS
    data, e.g. drawing Manhattan plots and running a fixed-effect
    meta-analysis.
